ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read &quot;The Child Samuel&quot; </div><div class="t mab2 x18 h28 y97e ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and &quot;Eli and His Sons&quot; in </div><div class="t m1df x43 h2c y596 ff6 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Patriarchs and Prophets, </div><div class="t m40f x8d h28 y596 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 569-580. If avail-</div><div class="t m6f5 x18 h28 y3bb ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">able, read the </div><div class="t me59 x19 h2c yf9c ff6 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SDA Bible Commentary </div><div class="t m36e x7 h28 y1514 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on 1 Samuel 1-3. Read the entire </div><div class="t m5f5 x18 h28 y185f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">text for today&apos;s lesson in several modem translations if possible. </div><div class="t m664 x18 h22 y170e ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m93 x19 h28 y1bcb ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In the same way that God called Samuel to the prophetic of-</div><div class="t m7db x18 h28 y1179 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fice, He calls each of us to fellowship with Himself and to service to His </div><div class="t ma20 x18 h28 y893 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">church and the world. When God calls me by name, am I ready to respond, </div><div class="t m808 x18 h28 y983 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Speak, Lord, for Your servant hears&quot;? </div><div class="t m105 x26 h22 y2143 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
